<div class="title">Glasto' 2000</div>
<div class="substance">Ecstasy & Amphetamines</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Maxxam&Exact=1">Maxxam</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Maxxam. "Glasto' 2000: An Experience with Ecstasy & Amphetamines (exp4492)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 23, 2001. erowid.org/exp/4492</div>

